comment.body:
Not reproduced with uBlock and AdGuard filters on my end. According to the report, you've enabled too many filters.
First, try to leave only ublock filters and EasyList + AdGuard - Ads, update them, clear browser data, restart it.
@AdamWr @BlazDT could you also take a look at this?

